After researching through reviews and determining that my player was region free I still had doubts about dropping 35 dollars on something that had a 50/50 chance of working. I took the risk and was highly impressed. Both Thor movies are included in their own cases. Both movies are no different than their US releases except a few minor difference on the cover and the case being the thickness of a PS4 game. Package was handle with care. No broken cases or loose discs during it's travels to my movie shelf

With the way Marvel is pumping out our favorite Super Hero movies these days,Don't waste your time getting DVD's separately anymore. Wait for the boxed sets like this one. You get two in one & pay the same amount of money. I like Thor - not as much as Captain America. I enjoyed the first one but in my typical pattern,I was disappointed & bored by the sequel. My husband  however,  is much easier to please & he found both equally entertaining. Because I got this as a gift for him & he liked it, I am giving  it 5 stars. If it were me,I would have given it a mid road 3 star rating because in my opinion,the sequel was not up to par.
